      • setData

        public void setData(org.ejml.data.DenseMatrix64F target,
                    double[][] data)

        Sets the data oftarget to that of the input matrix with the values and shape defined by the 2D array 'data'. It is assumed that 'data' has a row-major formatting:

        data[ row ][ column ]

        Parameters:
        target - 2D DenseMatrix. Modified to contain the values in 'data'.
        data - 2D array representation of the matrix. Not modified.
